description: Describes one or more of the tags for your Amazon ML object.

parameters.name: ResourceId
parameters.description: The ID of the ML object. For example, exampleModelId.

parameters.name: ResourceType
parameters.description: The type of the ML object.

nested_items.name: ResourceId
nested_items.description: The ID of the tagged ML object.

nested_items.name: ResourceType
nested_items.description: The type of the tagged ML object.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: A list of tags associated with the ML object.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the tag. Valid characters include Unicode letters, digits, white space, _, ., /, =, +, -, %, and @.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: An optional string, typically used to describe or define the tag. Valid characters include Unicode letters, digits, white space, _, ., /, =, +, -, %, and @.
